title: Mercer Granted Chapter of Phi Beta Kappa, Nation's Oldest and Most Prestigious Academic Honor Society ...
text: ( Source : Mercer University ) MACON - The nation's oldest and most prestigious academic honor society - Phi Beta Kappa - today approved the granting of a chapter to Mercer University during the organization's 44th Triennial Council in Denver ,
